---
title: Cajun Honey Chicken with Sticky Apricots, Quinoa and Balsamic Veggies
description: Sweet and spicy, our cajun chicken dinner is a winner! Originating from the US state of Louisiana, cajun spice is a distinct blend of paprika, garlic and cayenne pepper that brings this dish to life. Spicy chicken, sweet apricots and roasted vegetables with nutty light quinoa topped with sour cream and a little coriander.
